race.comment: SKY SPRINGER (8) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when third (28.84) at this track. Can find winning form. SCOTT AQUAPHOBIA (6) turned in a solid run last start over 500m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (28.68). Has a good record here at this journey. Must be included in calculations. MCIVOR MORGAN (3) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (28.84) in a Grade 5 at this track. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. OBSTROPALOUS (1) was below best last time at Sandown (30.42) in a Grade 5 NP, finishing a 11 length fourth. Has already won four times from this draw.
